    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for everything from grocery runs to weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s a fantastic, well-loved car that still has so much life left in it\u2014come check it out and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
