    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This 6-speed manual G96 transaxle example delivers raw engagement with a linear power band. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic upgrade, and the cooling system features a low-temp thermostat and metal-impeller water pump. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings for precise turn-in. While showing minor aerodynamic stone chips and light interior wear, the car is mechanically sound with documented service history and recent oil analysis. A high-performance entry into the 911 lineage for the serious driver.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
