    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking reliability and classic style. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts with precision. The exterior retains a beautiful gloss, showing only the minor character marks consistent with careful daily use. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free environment with supportive seating and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functioning exactly as they should. It has been garage-kept and recently detailed, ensuring it is ready for the road the moment you take the keys. A solid, dependable choice for anyone valuing quality and performance.",
