      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience and proven reliability. Meticulously maintained to rigorous standards, it remains in commendable condition, balancing aesthetic appeal with mechanical integrity. A premier choice for the discerning driver seeking exceptional value and long-term performance.",
      "price": 34800.0,
