    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs great, looks sharp, and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a solid ride that\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m happy to chat and answer any questions you might have, so don't be shy\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
