      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS unit has been overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced, addressing the platform's primary structural concerns. Power is sent through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry performs as intended. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain integrity and throttle response are exceptional.",
